OL,5,
OL,6,CG1982FA BBC TV news programme is
OL,7,Fpresented by two women for the first
OL,8,Ftime. Moira Stuart and Linda Alexander
OL,9,Fpresent News After Noon (BBC One).
OL,10,FAlexander was seconded from Newsnight
OL,11,Fto stand in for Richard Whitmore, who
OL,12,Fwas on leave for a week.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG1989FSir Robin Day presents Question
OL,15,FTime (BBC One) for the final time.
OL,16,
OL,17,CG2001FRichard Madeley and Judy
OL,18,FFinnigan present This Morning (ITV) for
OL,19,Fthe final time.
